{"about_the_game":"From the creators of CONARIUM, TRANSIENT, and the DARKNESS WITHIN series comes \u201cVeil of Madness,\u201d an eerie Lovecraftian deck-building game. Play as a Wiccarder, a member of a Chthonic religious order.  Build your deck, Card-battle with monsters, and embark on a quest to unravel the secrets surrounding the infamous Cromwell Mansion.<br><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2889330/extras/twitter_banner.png?t=1723388948\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2889330/extras/title_banner1.png?t=1723388948\" /><br>Gather unique cards along the way and upgrade them to improve their stats. Some cards can be found in secret areas, while others are only obtainable by completing certain quests. Therefore, pay attention to NPCs.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2889330/extras/gif1_small.gif?t=1723388948\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2889330/extras/title_banner2.png?t=1723388948\" /><br>You will encounter various creatures throughout the game. At times, you may need to battle more than one. Use your inventory strategically to survive.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2889330/extras/gif2_small.gif?t=1723388948\" />","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2889330/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1723388948","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2889330/page.bg.jpg?t=1723388948","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2889330/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1723388948","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2889330/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1723388948","c